metaTitle: Insight into Jhaptaal - Yogesh Samsi International Masterclass
metaDescription: This Masterclass provides an indepth insight into tabla solo repertoire in Jhaptaal (10 beat cycle).This is an opportunity to participate in an intensive workshop for talented young Tabla students by the world renowned Tabla player Yogesh Samsi, disciple of the late Ustad Allarakha and will be held on Saturday 6th July & Sunday 7th July 2024 via Zoom (Video conferencing & Webinar Platform).
title: Insight into Jhaptaal
heroImageAlt: Yogesh Samsi sitting with his tabla
